::Shadow Wing::

She saw Lunarpine and ran over to him.  She smiled slightly.
"I didn't kill them all so you could have some fun." Her wing was 
dripping mech fluid and she had cuts all over her body.
She looked down at herself.
"I suppose in the future that I shouldn't so overzelious?"
